---
import { getInvolvedLink } from "../shared-content/get-involved-link";
import Button from "../ui/button.astro";
---

<section class="w-full py-16">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] text-secondary">
        Coming Soon
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold text-primary md:text-4xl">
        Funding Futures
      </h1>
    </div>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-primary/80">
      We're preparing to launch initiatives that will mobilize alumni giving to
      support MNPS students and scholarships. This page will outline ways you
      can invest in the future of our graduates.
    </p>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-primary/80">
      Until then, you can join our network and be among the first to learn how
      to give and make an impact.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <Button href={getInvolvedLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Join the Alumni Network
      </Button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
